##As long as one of US lives, my 5-year-old daughter will not be an orphan

Micro-signal Xinminzhoukan

Function description, depth and angle —— this is what we can do.

Admission 12 days, I found the living room table of the two goldfish has not been fed, is still alive and well. Life is tenacious, man must be more tenacious than fish.

Dictation | Xiao Xincheng
Tidying | Wu Xue

Before this epidemic hit, I had envisioned my 2020: earn more money, honor the elderly, and take romantic outings with loved ones... but from that day on January 19, all good things came to an abrupt end, and I had only two words left on my wish list: Live.
Born in 1984, I am an ordinary Wuhan citizen, Xiao Xincheng is my social name, because I believe that "honesty is like gold" . In 2015, my wife, Zhan Xin, and I got married, bought a three bedroom house in the city and had a lovely daughter. That same year, I decided to resign from the bank and set up an IT supply chain management company with my senior brother. As a partner, I travel day and night, talking about clients do projects, 5 years, business has finally improved, a family of three live fairly substantial.
January 18, the weather in Wuhan is very cold, as usual, I go out after meals, check the next calendar before going out, there are 7 days to the New Year, touched the growing hair, decided to go to the familiar barber shop cut a inch. The Barber was very skillful and cut it off quickly. I waved goodbye and walked outside for another hour, when there were almost no face masks on the streets of Wuhan and everyone went about their business as usual.
A view of Xiao Xincheng from a residential area in Wuhan

At 9 pm, when I got home, I felt cold all over, accompanied by a little cough. My lover asked me if I had a cold. My temperature was normal, but I took a cold medicine to be safe. The next morning, the forehead began to burn, a 38 degrees Celsius, a fever. Because she works in a medical distribution company, she often sends test reagents to the Golden Pool Hospital and children's Hospital. She knows something. "You put on a mask, " she said with alarm. "I'll take you to the community for a shot. "
After the injection, my temperature dropped to a low grade fever of 37.5 °c the next day, which happened to be our company's annual meeting, because Zhong Nanshan had not yet mentioned the symptoms of human to human transmission, so I decided to wear a mask. At the annual meeting, I wear a mask did not take off, in the middle did not eat a meal, met toastmasters colleagues, I will also sideways drink. My colleagues said: "boss, this is too much. " At that time, we all feel fine.
I didn't think it would be that bad, but considering the health of my daughter and the mother-in-law who cared for the children, I isolated myself in the room. Meals were delivered to the door and shots were given at o'clock in the community. However, things did not go well. On the 22nd, my beloved also began to have a fever, because the community clinic was closed on the 24th Spring Festival, and the risk of cross-infection in the designated hospitals was high, so we decided to go to the nearby second-class hospital —————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————————— --.
Photo courtesy of fever clinic, Veterans Hospital, Hubei Province

The Va Hospital is only 1.1 km from my home and has a fever clinic. Arrived at the hospital, the person that see a doctor waited for a long line, but affirmation is not fixed-point admit a hospital person much. My wife and I scheduled a morning, blood, CT, and other results, and soon came out of the film, the results show: I have a serious infection in both lungs, my wife a lung infection. With the checklist, we're screwed.
On the same day, we were admitted as suspected patients. At first the hospital was quite flustered, and there was not much psychological preparation, nor was there a special isolation ward. Later, the hospital held a meeting to temporarily coordinate a ward into a new coronary pneumonia isolation ward, my wife and I are relatively lucky, is the 8th and 9th admitted.
When I got settled in, I immediately sent out a friend circle and told my friends and relatives, "I may have new pneumonia. Please pay attention, if you have a cold or fever, see a doctor immediately. " Frankly speaking, after I was admitted to the hospital, my mood fluctuated greatly, we all have the fear of the unknown. It's a joke to say you're not afraid to die. Mother-in-law with her daughter at home is also very anxious, I have been calling my wife, said the two people cried, the topic of conversation is mostly "if not cured, how to do" , "how to become an orphan children do? "
Photo provided by interviewees at the admission window of Hubei Provincial Veterans Hospital

As the pillar of the family, my heart is particularly not taste, I advised myself not to fall, now that the matter has been so, then put their confidence in the doctor, trust the doctor. As long as one of me and the one I love lives, my 5-year-old daughter won't be an orphan. After thinking it over, I still made the worst plan, put the family property disk, the account of the after death, and, wrote a suicide note. In fact, when you begin to accept death with equanimity, your mind changes a lot.
The next day, I told my mother-in-law and friends, if there is no bad news, do not call, no news, is the best news. My partner and I began to encourage each other to focus on fighting the disease. A day infusion 10 hours, play more, hand full of needle eye, sometimes the needle walked, the whole hand is swollen. And at that time, the hospital has no food service, the family meals to the hospital elevator every day, the nurse to pick up.
On New Year's Eve, Xiao Xincheng and his wife Watch CCTV New Year's Gala at the hospital

Doctors are trying to deal with the new virus. Five days before admission, doctors in accordance with anti-bacterial and anti-viral treatment program, hit the CEPHALOSPORIN and other antibiotics. After two days of treatment, my body temperature went from a low grade fever of 37.7 °C to a high fever of 38 °C or even close to 39 °C, because I was good at biology before, and knew that once I had an infusion, it must be a process in which my immunity was destroyed, so did not think at all: "Why more and more powerful. "
In the Guanggu district of Wuhan's Third Hospital, a doctor at the Shanghai Fourth People's Hospital in Wuhan, China, examines his wife, Zhan Xin

On the fifth day of hospitalization, NUCLEIC ACID test results came out, we were diagnosed as new coronary pneumonia, I was weak positive, love is positive. Due to the limited medical conditions in the war hospital, my lover was transferred to Guanggu Hospital District of Wuhan Third Hospital (hereinafter referred to as: Wuhan Third Hospital Guanggu Hospital district) , my mood suddenly fell to the bottom of the valley. Although I do not let family contact her, but I sent her wechat every day, said are encouraging words. My lover told me that Wuhan Sanyuan Guanggu Hospital District Treatment Program is different, no injection, is to take medicine. The doctor tells to eat hydrochloric acid aweiduo er piece and Lianhua Qing Wen capsule, eat a meal more next, increase nutrition.
Fortunately, from the fifth day, I began to reduce the fever, every day with a towel to wipe out a lot of sweat. My lover sent me a wechat message saying: "You must cure first, then I can have hope. " The hospital also solved the problem of eating. To avoid cross-infection, the nurse delivered three meals a day, and the menu was also very rich, at least two eggs a day, and half a chicken, fish, vegetables and so on. The doctor told repeatedly, even if no appetite, also want to eat more protein, improve immunity.
Yeah, but it's hard to keep a good attitude when it comes to this kind of thing. After the transfer of loved ones, next to the bed to a 50-year-old uncle, was in the family dinner infection, now a family of 8 people were all admitted to the hospital. Uncle was very worried. He had to take his temperature countless times a day. He was always worried about his body. "What's with the temp? It's 38 again. " "Why am I breathing again? Am I sick? " "I'm not sick. Why are there so many vials? "
Photo provided by interviewees in isolation ward of Kwong Valley Hospital, Wuhan No. 3 Hospital

I am a kind of "come over" , know that the fever must have a repeated process, uncle older point of negative emotions, but also normal, I tried to help him resolve. Since January 22nd, I have been deeply impressed by the hard work of the medical staff. Because of the large number of patients, the bedside call bell did not stop all day, one after another. All the hospital doctors, nurses did not go home for more than 10 days, every day to rescue patients, transfusion are used to run, with "war" no difference.
The nurse in charge of our bed said she wore a protective suit for six days and wore a mask to bed at night so as not to waste supplies. Once, she pricked the wrong needle, very nervous, but also hurriedly apologize, I especially understand her. As a patient, should understand with the medical staff, do not increase their burden, can solve their own solution. In fact, they and patients, are facing great psychological pressure. This time, the whole country sent many medical teams to support Wuhan. In the Guanggu Hospital District of Wuhan Sanyuan where my wife lives, there are doctors from the Shanghai Fourth People's Hospital, the Rehabilitation Hospital affiliated to Shanghai Tongji University and the Oriental Hospital affiliated to Tongji University. On January 30th, under their care, the lover's fever broke.
Zhan Xin poses with doctors at the Tongji University for a picture

February 1, the ninth day of admission, my temperature has been more than 70 hours to maintain normal, color recovery is good, from the beginning of supporting up, to sit up very naturally now. The doctor said, observe a few more days, if nothing unusual, perhaps can be discharged. I am very happy, listening to the birds outside, the heart of the haze all of a sudden blown away. For the last three days, I've been taking blood, getting a C.T. , waiting for results, eating. At 11 a.m. on February 3rd, the doctor officially discharged me.
I posted on my facebook page the first time, and everyone was so excited. I reported the news to the community and the property, the driver on duty said he did not dare to pick up, I expressed understanding, because in the community under the jurisdiction of dozens of buildings, there are more than 40 confirmed and suspected cases, including 2 properties were also infected. In the afternoon after the discharge formalities, told me to rest, and finally I walked home. That day, I walked in the streets of Wuhan, the sun is particularly good.
Soon to be discharged from the hospital recovery of Xiao Xincheng released a circle of friends

On Feb. 8, the Lantern Festival, my beloved was also discharged from the hospital, and the Guanggu district of Wuhan Sanyuan also held a farewell ceremony. The one wearing a black down jacket on the news photo was my beloved, along with six other patients suffering from new coronary pneumonia. On the day of discharge from the hospital, shen Yanmei, a nurse in charge of beds at Tongji University's Rehabilitation Hospital, wrote this: "today, three patients in our ward have been cured, including my sister Zhan, who is in charge of bed 39. This is the first group of patients that I have cured since I came to Wuhan. After more than 10 days of hard work, I finally have been rewarded. "
Zhan Xin poses with Yan Mei Shen, the chief nurse of the Tongji University, for a photo

Photo by Zhan Xin (seventh from left) of the first batch of cured patients in Guanggu district, the Third Hospital of Wuhan

After 12 full days in the hospital, we were especially thankful to the doctors and nurses, and to the community and the property. My wife and I were the lucky ones, compared to the severely ill patients who were still in quarantine. Fortunately, my daughter and my mother-in-law are healthy after 17 days of isolation, and my colleagues and friends are healthy under house observation. I don't like to post on my facebook page, and I don't like to tell stories about myself. The reason I want to share this time is to tell my friends who are in the "dark" , don't just see the sadness, don't just think the worst, put yourself in the hands of a doctor, beat the disease, and be done with it.
Back at home, I was reunited with my family. For the next 14 days, I assigned a special lesson to myself and my partner: Walk more than 5,000 steps a day in my room, practice boxing for 10 minutes, three eggs a day, some vegetables, and wear a mask at all times. Admission 12 days, I found the living room table of the two goldfish has not been fed, is still alive and well. Life is tenacious, man must be more tenacious than fish.
Xiao Xincheng after discharge from the hospital in the friend Circle Sun picture caption: People must be tougher than fish, interviewees for the picture
